msg.payload.title = global.get("flex_name")

return msg;

name: why?
info:
We need to delay Antenna Genius commands 
because when we switch ports on the Flex Radio,
it sometimes causes the Antenna Genius 
to react by changing antenna configs,
so we need to wait for that to happen before
sending new commands and bring the switch back
to the state we want it to have.

name: README ‚Ä¢ Rotor control for PSTRotatorAZ
info:
This flow requires PSTRotatorAZ version 13.89 or newer. 

Tested on PSTRotator AZ 14.17

PSTRotatorAZ needs to have UDP server enabled.

Change the UDP out node to the IP address of computer running PSTRotatorAZ.

---

Based on work from Dave WO2X and Tormod LA9VKA.

This particular iteration comes from Sebastian KI2D and focuses on making
more efficient use of space.
* Improves map behavior.
* Adds azimuth display inside the map.
* Allows clicking inside the beam for finetuning of AZ.
* Allows clicking on target az to stop movement.
* Allows scaling of widget.
